out-of-the-month-for-january-2014</ref>\n**2014 July Knockout of the Month <small>vs. [[Jim Miller (fighter)|Jim Miller]]</small><ref>http://mmajunkie.com/2014/08/mmajunkies-knockout-of-the-month-for-july-2014</ref>\n*'''[[Sherdog|Sherdog Awards]]'''\n**2009 Fight of the Year <small>vs. [[Benson Henderson]] on October 10</small>\n**2008 Round of the Year <small>vs. [[Rob McCullough]] on November 5; Round 1</small>\n*'''[[Sports Illustrated]]'''\n**2009 Fight of the Year <small>vs. [[Benson Henderson]] on October 10</small>\n*'''[[World MMA Awards]]'''\n**2011 [[World MMA Awards#Breakthrough Fighter of the Year|Breakthrough Fighter of the Year]]\n\n==Mixed martial arts record==\n\n{{MMArecordbox\n| draws= \n| nc= 1\n| ko-wins= 10\n| sub-wins= 17\n| dec-wins= 9\n| ko-losses=7\n| sub-losses= 1\n| dec-losses= 6\n| dq-wins= \n| dq-losses= \n| other-wins= \n| other-losses= \n}}\n{{MMA record start}}\n|-\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|align=center|36\u201314 (1)\n|[[Conor McGregor]]\n|TKO (head kick and punches)<!--Result as per Sherdog.com-->\n|[[UFC 246]] \n|{{dts|2020|January|18}}\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0:40\n|[[Las Vegas, Nevada]], United States\n|{{small|Welterweight bout.}}\n|-\n|{{no2||align=|style=|color=}}Loss\n|align=center|36\u201313 (1)\n|[[Justin Gaethje]]\n|TKO (punches)\n|[[UFC Fight Night: Cowboy vs. Gaethje]] \n|{{dts|2019|September|14}}\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|4:18\n|[[Vancouver, British Columbia]], Canada\n|\n|-\n|{{no2||align=|style=|color=}}Loss\n|align=center|36\u201312 (1)\n|[[Tony Ferguson]]\n|TKO (doctor stoppage)\n|[[UFC 238]] \n|{{dts|2019|June|8}}\n|align=center|2\n|align=center|5:00\n|[[Chicago, Illinois]], United States\n|{{small|Fight of the Night.}}\n|-\n|{{yes2||align=|style=|color=}}Win\n|align=center|36\u201311 (1)\n|[[Al Iaquinta]]\n|Decision (unanimous)\n|[[UFC Fight Night: Iaquinta vs. Cowboy]] \n|{{dts|2019|May|4}}\n|align=center|5\n|align=center|5:00\n|[[Ottawa, Ontario]], Canada\n|{{small|Fight of the Night.}}\n|-\n|{{yes2||align=