oons]]\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| [[UFC 160]]\n| {{dts|2013|May|25}}\n| align=center| 3\n| align=center| 5:00\n| [[Las Vegas, Nevada]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{no2||align=|style=|color=}}Loss\n| align=center| 19\u20135 (1)\n| [[Anthony Pettis]]\n| KO (kick to the body)\n| [[UFC on Fox: Johnson vs. Dodson]]\n| {{dts|2013|January|26}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2:35\n| [[Chicago, Illinois]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{yes2||align=|style=|color=}}Win\n| align=center| 19\u20134 (1)\n| [[Melvin Guillard]]\n| KO (head kick and punch)\n| [[UFC 150]]\n| {{dts|2012|August|11}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 1:16\n| [[Denver, Colorado]], United States\n| {{small|Catchweight (157.5 lbs) bout; Guillard missed weight. Knockout of the Night. Fight of the Night.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2||align=|style=|color=}}Win\n| align=center| 18\u20134 (1)\n| [[Jeremy Stephens]]\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| [[2012 in UFC#UFC on Fuel TV: Korean Zombie vs. Poirier|UFC on Fuel TV: Korean Zombie vs. Poirier]]\n| {{dts|2012|May|15}}\n| align=center| 3\n| align=center| 5:00\n| [[Fairfax, Virginia]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{no2||align=|style=|color=}}Loss\n| align=center| 17\u20134 (1)\n| [[Nate Diaz]]\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| [[UFC 141]]\n| {{dts|2011|December|30}}\n| align=center| 3\n| align=center| 5:00\n| [[Las Vegas, Nevada]], United States\n| {{small|Fight of the Night.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2||align=|style=|color=}}Win\n| align=center| 17\u20133 (1)\n| [[Dennis Siver]]\n| Submission (rear-naked choke)\n| [[UFC 137]]\n| {{dts|2011|October|29}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2:22\n| [[Las Vegas, Nevada]], United States\n| {{small|Submission of the Night.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2||align=|style=|color=}}Win\n| align=center| 16\u20133 (1)\n| [[Charles Oliveira]]\n| TKO (punches)\n| [[UFC Live: Hardy vs. Lytle]]\n| {{dts|2011|August|14}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 3:01\n| [[Milwaukee, Wisconsin]], United States\n| {{small|Knockout of the Night.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2||align=|style=|color=}}Win\n| a