d2|White|Notes |border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n|}\n\n==Professional boxing record==\n{{BoxingRecordSummary\n|ko-losses=1\n}}\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:95%\"\n|-\n!{{abbr|No.|Number}}\n!Result\n!Record\n!Opponent\n!Method\n!Round, time\n!Date\n!Location\n!Notes\n|-\n|1\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|0\u20131\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Geoffrey Spruiell\n|{{abbr|TKO|Technical knockout}}\n|2 (4), {{small|2:39}}\n|Nov 21, 2003\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Los Caporales Regency Hotel, [[Denver, Colorado]], U.S.}}\n|\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n\n* [[List of current UFC fighters]]\n* [[List of male mixed martial artists]]\n* [[Muay Thai]]\n* [[List of male kickboxers]]\n* [[Boxing]]\n\n== References ==\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cerrone, Donald}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American male mixed martial artists]]\n[[Category:American sportspeople of Italian descent]]\n[[Category:American male kickboxers]]\n[[Category:American Muay Thai practitioners]]\n[[Category:American practitioners of Brazilian jiu-jitsu]]\n[[Category:People awarded a black belt in Brazilian jiu-jitsu]]\n[[Category:American sportspeople in doping cases]]\n[[Category:Boxers from Colorado]]\n[[Category:Doping cases in mixed martial arts]]\n[[Category:Kickboxers from Colorado]]\n[[Category:Lightweight mixed martial artists]]\n[[Category:Mixed martial artists from Colorado]]\n[[Category:People from El Paso County, Colorado]]\n[[Category:Middleweight boxers]]\n[[Category:Middleweight kickboxers]]\n[[Category:American male boxers]]\n[[Category:Ultimate Fighting Championship male fighters]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American mixed martial arts fighter}}\n{{Infobox martial artist\n| name            = Donald Cerrone\n| image           = VCJCS hosts USO Spring Tour 160312-D-HU462-263.jpg\n| image_size      = \n| caption         = Cerrone in 2016\n| birth_name      = Donald Anthony Cerrone\n| other_names     = Cowboy \n| birth_date      = 